'''Riders of Rohan''' can refer to:

*a common name for the [[Rohirrim]], the horsemen from the north who dwelt in the land of [[Rohan]] after its foundation by [[Eorl the Young]].
* ''[[The Riders of Rohan]]'', a chapter of ''[[The Two Towers]]''

*''[[Riders of Rohan (1985 book)|Riders of Rohan]]'', a game supplement for [[Middle-earth Role Playing]].
*''[[J.R.R. Tolkien's Riders of Rohan|Riders of Rohan]]'', a [[1990]] video game.
*''[[The Lord of the Rings Online: Riders of Rohan]]'', the fourth expansion for ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online]]''.

* ''[[The Riders of Rohan (scene)|The Riders of Rohan]]'', the eleventh scene of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''
* ''[[The Riders of Rohan (soundtrack)|The Riders of Rohan]]'', track #3 on ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers - Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''.
